    "title": "京东规则动态一览（2025年2月24日-2025年2月28日）",
    "followRuleId": "1211216294599331840",
    "content": "<p style=\"margin: 0cm; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">各位商家：</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; background: white; font-variant-ligatures: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">本周共公示9条规则，生效6条规则，新增2条规则解读。</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; background: white; font-variant-ligatures: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">具体内容如下，可点击查阅：</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 16.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">【规则公示】</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: blue;\">1</span><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: blue;\">、新增《</span><a href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1212603192479715328&amp;btype=1\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: blue;\">京东开放平台五金/</span><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: blue;\">工具类目销售激励政策（2025.3.1-2025.3.31</span><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: blue;\">）</span></a><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #0000ff;\">》</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">核心变更点：在激励周期内，若店铺入驻时间&gt;3个月，且店铺在五金/工具类目下有效销售额达到相关标准，将给予一定奖励。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: blue;\">2</span><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: blue;\">、修订</span><a href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1211913016082305024\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: blue;\">《京东开放平台电脑办公/</span><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: blue;\">文教文化用品类目资质标准》</span></a></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">核心变更点：<span style=\"color: black;\">电脑办公部分类目调整为允许小规模纳税人入驻。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: blue;\">3</span><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: blue;\">、</span><a href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1211629013307625472&amp;btype=1\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: blue;\">关于修订《京东开放平台经营类目商品阈值明细表》的公示通知</span></a></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">核心变更点：<span style=\"color: black;\">1</span><span style=\"color: black;\">）新增7个二级类目阈值；2）调整5个二级类目阈值。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">关联规则：</span><a href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1211622812805107712&amp;btype=12\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: blue;\">京东开放平台个人/</span><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: blue;\">个体经营类目商品阈值明细表</span></a></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: blue;\">4</span><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: blue;\">、</span><a href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1211560627345166336&amp;btype=1\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: blue;\">关于修订《京东开放平台店铺综合体验分规则》的公示通知</span></a><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"> </span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">核心变更点：1）物流履约因子项指标调整；2）五星店铺认证规则调整。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: blue;\">5</span><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: blue;\">、</span><a href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1211584136112902144&amp;btype=12\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: blue;\">关于修订《京东开放平台个人/</span><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: blue;\">个体店铺综合体验分规则》的公示通知</span></a></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">核心变更点：物流履约因子项指标调整。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: blue;\">6</span><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: blue;\">、</span><a href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1211241957188308992&amp;btype=14\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: blue;\">关于修订《新品ICON</span><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: blue;\">管理规则》的公示通知</span></a></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">核心变更点：调整新品定义、打标要求及打标方式。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: blue;\">7</span><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: blue;\">、</span><a href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1212715008157421568&amp;btype=1\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: blue;\">关于修订《京东开放平台不当发布商品或信息细则》、《京东开放平台商家违规管理总则》的公示通知</span></a></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">核心变更点：新增<span style=\"color: black; background: #F8F8F9;\">对违规商品/信息的处置措施</span>。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><a href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1212731056730542080&amp;btype=12\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: blue;\">8</span><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: blue;\">、关于修订《京东开放平台个人/</span><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: blue;\">个体合规管理规则》的公示通知</span></a></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">核心变更点：新增<span style=\"color: black; background: #F8F8F9;\">对违规商品/信息的处置措施</span>。 </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: blue;\">9</span><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: blue;\">、新增《</span><a href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1212644745470414848&amp;btype=1\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: blue;\">京东开放平台优惠权益工具违约金收取比例调整</span></a><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: blue;\">》</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">核心变更点：商家需在2025年5月31日前完成2024 年权益工具开票核销工作，如截至 2025 年 5 月 31 日仍未完成，将对未完成核销部分的金额收取违约金，且京东对未核销部分的违约金比例统一调整至 30%。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 16.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">【规则生效】</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1</span><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、</span><a href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1208967395511767040&amp;btype=1\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: blue;\">关于新增《瑞士表/</span><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: blue;\">德表准入品牌明细》的公示通知</span></a></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">核心变更点：新增关于当前可入驻开店的瑞士表、德表类品牌明细清单。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2</span><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、</span><a href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1210107352817209344&amp;btype=1\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: blue;\">关于修订《京东开放平台店铺命名规则》的公示通知</span></a></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">核心变更点：</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1)</span><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">新增品牌名称与企业商号重复场景的专卖店命名形式；</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2)</span><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">调整店铺名称违反规则更名时的注意事项。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">3</span><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、</span><a href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1209676850964598784&amp;btype=1\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: blue;\">关于新增《京东开放平台结算周期规则》的公示通知</span></a></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">核心变更点： 新增关于结算周期的各类场景与说明。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">4</span><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、</span><a href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1208722953223671808&amp;btype=12\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: blue;\">关于修订《京东开放平台个人/</span><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: blue;\">个体合规管理规则》的公示通知</span></a></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">核心变更点： 增加不当发布商品或信息中&ldquo;品牌错误使用&rdquo;的违规情形和处理措施 。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">5</span><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、</span><a href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1208689859091369984&amp;btype=12\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: blue;\">关于修订《京东开放平台个人/</span><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: blue;\">个体纠纷处理规则》的公示通知</span></a></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">核心变更点： 增加商家补充证据的时效要求。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">6</span><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、</span><a href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1208652768164843520&amp;btype=1\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: blue;\">关于修订《京东开放平台运费问题纠纷处理标准》的公示通知</span></a></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">核心变更点： 增加关于商家寄回地址产生运费争议问题的标准 。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 16.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">【规则解读】</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><a style=\"color: blue; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1212326802786226176&amp;btype=15\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">1、店铺综合体验分规则常见问题解答</span></a></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: le